                      "blocks": {
                        "text_PnX4xD": {
                          "type": "text",
                          "settings": {
                            "text": "<p>We know you’re looking forward to your order, and we’re here<br/>to help you track it down. There are a few reasons your delivery may be taking<br/>a little longer than expected.</p><p>Your order may still be in transit, especially during peak<br/>periods or promotional events when dispatch times can be slightly extended.<br/>It’s also worth checking your tracking details, as your parcel may be delayed<br/>with the carrier or awaiting delivery.</p><p>If your order includes multiple items, they may arrive<br/>separately depending on availability.</p><p>For the most up-to-date information, we recommend checking<br/>your shipping confirmation email or tracking link. If you still need<br/>assistance, our Customer Care team will be happy to help.</p>",
                            "width": "100%",
